snippet.title: Mars After Midnight - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Mars’ citizens need your help! Mars After Midnight is a silly entrant-screening, mess-tidying, session-planning work simulator for Playdate developed by Lucas Pope.
Get it now on Catalog: https://play.date/games/mars-after-midnight/
